{"tid":1988024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎：追蹤病毒源頭　中方拒國際專家獨立調查","createTime":"2020-04-25T02:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T03:15:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7dca7d0fc321394b682be712cf4a770e053c74f","tid":1988024,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒周六（24日）報道，中國駐英公使陳雯受訪時稱，中方不會同意讓國際專家到中國就新冠病毒的源頭展開獨立調查，認為有關要求是出於政治目的，而且會分散中國防疫的專注力。<br />\n<br />\n陳雯表示，有關新冠病毒源頭的傳聞很多，但這種錯誤信息非常危險，全球正全力應對新冠肺炎疫情，認為在此時提及要調查病毒源頭，不僅會分散防疫的注意力，更將防疫資源轉移。<br />\n<br />\n駐英大使劉曉明日前否認中國隱瞞疫情，所謂的掩蓋及隱藏疫情的猜測和虛假訊息都並非事實，暗指部分國家有先入為主的偏見，呼籲西方媒體要秉持平衡及客觀的立場報道。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200425/bkn-20200425090421029-0425_00952_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"545fffc7f7a346003c99fca4fb473af31d6d19c2","tid":1988024,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:03:38.000Z","msg":"會分散搞香港注意力"},{"pid":"7f6c173b6293820171e7d023ace7321824a94958","tid":1988024,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>明曬！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0453fd1bbad63e95106d38c02981e49152e466d0","tid":1988024,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:04:23.000Z","msg":"成立獨立調查委員會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3103911/org/5cce8ebcee39d2ee88d34aa10347ce5e.jpg/vBLrdE3Gq8DJNBLlgGM30BBvgH_UZTa9uHwtZLh8LWQ?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3103911%2Forg%2F5cce8ebcee39d2ee88d34aa10347ce5e.jpg%2FvBLrdE3Gq8DJNBLlgGM30BBvgH_UZTa9uHwtZLh8LWQ%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=5fd3676b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd5ffde4c0cdc1327c6517490c7c21ce59a795f7","tid":1988024,"uid":123970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:07:31.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩畀人查？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梗係收咗美國佬錢心虛啦。"},{"pid":"51cb14cd8988233bfc208ac6ac22bb1c4fab4ae1","tid":1988024,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"咁撚辛苦整隻支那肺炎出黎，點會比你知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042717536640395a73f8dbeb54c0c9c4cf2bca96","tid":1988024,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"洗撚查咩，問連登仔就知啦，烚吓烚吓仲話專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca64f4a77e1094bcf3354ab3af480f7e95c14fb","tid":1988024,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:15:05.000Z","msg":"大佬啊 ! 點比你地獨立調查得架 ?  就好似香港 32000 名恐怖分子, 一樣唔撚查得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}